---
globs: components/*/index.tsx
alwaysApply: false
---
When working on new UI components or larger changes to existing components in this repository, follow the workflow in **CREATE.md** at the repository root (you can attach it as `@CREATE.md`).

If the user wants to **create a new** component and **did not give its name**, ask them first for the name and the matching kebab-case folder under `components/`; do not implement without that.
